Chiselled into the wall above the great
vault, half-eaten by lichen:
$HERE SLEEPS NO ONE.
$WEEP NOT AT THE EMPTY BED.
$BAR THE DOOR. SALT THE SILL.
$AND PRAY THE DAWN COMES SWIFTLY.
#end
