A brass plaque, tarnished nearly black.
You rub it clean with your sleeve.
$"TO WHOEVER READS THIS -
$ the garlic is your only mercy.
$ Take it. Take all of it.
$ He counts his dead, and he will
$ notice one braid missing sooner
$ than he notices you."
Signed only: a groundskeeper who left.
#end
