$THE OUBLIETTE
$of the Crimson Count
The chains here have held men until men were
only chains.

The way onward is not a door you will find by
touching walls at random. Somewhere among these
cells one stone remembers how to move.

Bring light. The Count keeps none for guests.
#end
    end
